HEADWORD: Entourage
<hw>En`tou`rage"</hw> <pr>(⟦aum⟧N`t⟦oomac⟧`r⟦adot⟧zh")</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>Surroundings; specif., collectively,
